DataElement.preferredDefinition: An explanatory or critical comment, or other in-context information (e.g., pattern, motif, link), that has been associated with data or other types of information.:The usual or expected function of something; the part something plays in an action or event.:An independently existing thing (living or nonliving)._A sentence of inquiry that asks for a reply; a request for information (e.g., a formal request to a database or search engine).:A coded value specifying an identifiable class of an entity or activity based on common qualities._Reference concept defined by a referenced code system.
